  64:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****  *
  65:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****  * The %Matrix class is the work-horse for all \em dense (\ref dense "note") matrices and vectors w
  66:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****  * Vectors are matrices with one column, and row-vectors are matrices with one row.
