 142:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****  * when the exact numbers of rows and columns are not known at compile-time, but it is known at com
 143:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****  * cannot exceed a certain value. This happens when taking dynamic-size blocks inside fixed-size ma
 144:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****  * MaxRows_ and MaxCols_ are the dimensions of the original matrix, while Rows_ and Cols_ are Dynam
 145:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****  * </dl>
